## Task
For every candidate label listed above, decide whether it satisfies the rubric
criteria overall (`passed`: true or false), optionally assign a continuous
`score` in the range [0.0, 1.0], and give a one-sentence `reason`. Evaluate
each candidate independently — do not rank or compare candidates against one
another, only against the rubric criteria.
